title: Interview w/ Billionaire Jeff Hoffman
itunes:title: Interview w/ Billionaire Jeff Hoffman
description:
Episode 312 - Ever wanted to know how a billionaire got to where they are? In this episode I interview Jeff Hoffman, who is the billionaire co-founder of Priceline.com. He is a wealth of knowledge and you will learn a ton from just listening to the way he thinks and the way he works.
